  rdfs:comment           "Provides Input For Rule. The relation 'ELAC2 cleaves the 3' end of pre-tRNA' 'null' 'TRNT1 polymerizes CCA at the 3' end of pre-tRNA' was inferred because:\n reaction1 has an output that is an input of reaction 2. " , "Imported from Reactome: https://reactome.org/content/detail/R-HSA-6784531" ;
